          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A 25 MeV collimated beam of neutrons produced by",
                "bombarding a Ti-T target with a 8 MeV pulsed deuteron",
                "beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COIN",
                "MWPC",
                "MWPC",
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SCIN",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Two MWPC's, one placed behind the entrance- and one",
                "before the exit-window of the deuterium gas cell, pro-",
                "vided anticoincidence and coincidence signals respec-",
                "tively to the telescope scintillators as to ensure",
                "that all signals have their origin within the gas cell.",
                "The distance (flight path) between the two telescope",
                "scintillation counters (delta-E and stop-detector) was",
                "42.3 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The tritons are distinguished from other",
                "particles by time-of flight between both scintillator",
                "detectors and by the energy deposit in the stop-",
                "detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In order to separate the 25 MeV neutrons from the",
                "prompt gamma-rays and the continuum part of the neutron",
                "spectrum the time between the signal of the pulsing",
                "system and that of the delta-E-scintillator was",
                "measured. By setting a time window the 25 MeV neutrons",
                "were selected."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The area of the tritons in the TOF versus energy spec-",
                "trum overlaps sligthly that of the deuterons. In order",
                "to evaluate the number of measured tritons the events",
                "of equal-time distance to the deuteron band were",
                "summed up. The number of tritons was evaluated from",
                "a 6-parameter fit for the resulting triton and deu-",
                "teron distributions."
              ]
            }
          ],
